verbose_text: The SSA assay revealed that all sgRNAs that were highly active in the in vitro assay [Rnf10, Nalcn, Dnase1/2 (E2), Dnase1/2 (E7), Ap4e1, Nxn, Dbn1, and Asic4] induced the expression of firefly luciferase to levels comparable to the AAVS1 control; however, the two sgRNAs with less in vitro activity also showed somewhat lower activity in the transfection assay.
